## =============================================================================
## Navigation
## =============================================================================

@prefix nav: <urn:reckons:docs/nav/> .

nav:BackToHub
    rdf:type            ktype:Document ;
    rdfs:label          "Back to Documentation Hub" ;
    skos:definition     "Return to the main documentation hub with all leap nodes and the Reckons.AI story." ;
